{"tid":547724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"24歲女見習律師-太古城墮樓殞命","createTime":"2018-02-01T17:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T12:35:04.000Z","uid":121464,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"75296c13d6d19913cc88420bc83dd51e64dc9c75","tid":547724,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:30:14.000Z","msg":"昨(2月1日)深夜11時許，一名女子在港島東太古城順安閣高處墮下，保安見狀報警求助。救護員趕至現場，發現女事主已奄奄一息，立即為其急救，並送往東區醫院搶救，惟最終證實不治。據悉女死者姓韋(24歲)，警方正調查事件起因。據悉事主與家人同住上址一單位，事發時獨自走上天台，躍下輕生。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，死者生前任職見習律師，在中環一所律師行工作。她持有香港中文大學法學專業證書，及為該校法律榮譽學士畢業。<br />\n<br />\nsource: hk01<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nrip"},{"pid":"8a8fcd9b28f28405dc40bd87e8a0c591d69f2b73","tid":547724,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:30:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0040a8d6d182f915b6d464c2d4ef96e86987aac8","tid":547724,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:31:15.000Z","msg":"做到律師都要跳"},{"pid":"bb7cc3ee56943b549c9f3727eb359e7a0f78c4fc","tid":547724,"uid":16425,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0040a8d6d182f915b6d464c2d4ef96e86987aac8","tid":547724,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:31:15.000Z","msg":"做到律師都要跳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"可能好大壓力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1a450198977595e958d7d0ff31a17abb09af65","tid":547724,"uid":45353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:32:21.000Z","msg":"尋晚仲突然諗天氣凍係咪會小d人自殺"},{"pid":"caae7c50a52425563dfd6bc6c7d3c44fac96f9af","tid":547724,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:32:29.000Z","msg":"太古城都jump😑q"},{"pid":"653559ccbae976a2bf979e1bacfb5d895a8d51ac","tid":547724,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0040a8d6d182f915b6d464c2d4ef96e86987aac8","tid":547724,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2